{"tid":993650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"觀塘老婦樓梯仆倒受傷　昏迷送院","createTime":"2019-01-24T05:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T08:04:52.000Z","uid":41404,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"28b781c07ddfb4553f4726f166811aa97a4cab17","tid":993650,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T05:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190124/photo/bkn-20190124110104175-0124_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190124124922\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190124%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190124110104175-0124_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190124124922&h=82ca938e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老婦仆倒地上受傷送院。(讀者提供)<br />\n<br />\n觀塘開源道中國銀行(香港)分行對開，今早(24日)10時許，一名姓黃(77歲)老婦疑「差錯腳」，由約1呎高的梯級上跌落地面，以致頭部流血受傷，陷入昏迷，有熱心途人及銀行職員見狀，立即上前協助及報警。救護員趕抵，立即將老婦送院，經搶救後恢復知覺。警方調查後，列作有人意外受傷處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190124/mobile/bkn-20190124110104175-0124_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190124%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190124110104175-0124_00822_001.html&d=7jr721pX1FVco0rX7P5j%2BG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=b4aef4b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190124/mobile/bkn-20190124110104175-0124_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f1970efb6847af3acc3d4f30465a69aa1ae1fd28","tid":993650,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T05:43:49.000Z","msg":"趕住換新銀紙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6bdf56c59103e1b2bb335111dc97e8a42edb1c1","tid":993650,"uid":78791,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T05:43:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fbe3a2e66796da37940642114d62cd488b89bd6","tid":993650,"uid":3302,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T05:45:07.000Z","msg":"死廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90a33f0baa5a07f7